Class KeyValueMasterClientServiceHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • tachyon.master.keyvalue.KeyValueMasterClientServiceHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    KeyValueMasterClientService.Iface, TachyonService.Iface

    @ThreadSafe
public final class KeyValueMasterClientServiceHandler
extends Object
implements KeyValueMasterClientService.Iface
    This class is a Thrift handler for key-value master RPCs invoked by a Tachyon client.
